Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Yo! Commandant, what are you doing here sneaking around?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Wow... I thought you were spying on something top secret but what's so interesting about Lee? Just go in and say hi... Hi! Lee!!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'You were busy with something and I saw Commandant here peeking for a while now.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Commandant, care to explain why you were loitering outside my room?', 4: '2'}
{2: "I didn't want to disturb you.", 3: '13', 4: 'I was just passing by.', 5: '13'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "...Just let me know next time, I wouldn't bar you from entering.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'See, I told you to just go and say hi!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "But I'm curious about what you were doing too.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "Don't you two have a mission to do or something other than spying on me?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Checking up on your wellbeing is also my job.', 3: '19'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "...Look all you want, I'm quite sure you'll lose interest soon enough.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "What about me? I'm interested even if Commandant isn't!", 4: '1'}
